:"完全没有生气……\n而且她每天都在看仓库演出的视频……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"是吗，那就太好了。\n奶奶也很乐在其中啊——","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"那么，大家今天也以下一次演出为目标，\n一起练习吧！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"话说，香澄……\n下次的演出已经决定下来了吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"你在说什么啊~？之前老师不是说了吗！\n『下次，能不能在学校演出？』\n你忘了吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"不，忘倒是没有忘，\n但那不就是句客套话吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"嗯？客套话……是什么？\n诶？我不懂","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙绫","body":"没事没事，因为这种话和香澄是八竿子打不着的。\n而且我觉得老师的话，肯定不是客套话","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev41-ep1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"不过确实，她也不是会说\n那种客套话的老师……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"ch